          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "type": "西皮摇板",
          "text": "倘若是再讲情儿自刎头来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "type": "stage",
          "text": "孔怀下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔凤英",
